dialogue.speaker: Doctor
dialogue.text: I thought I had this tuxedo thing figured out, but what the heck is this?

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: Oh, that's the number buzzle. You wear it on your head like a sweatband.

dialogue.speaker: Doctor
dialogue.text: Then you clip your pens and pencils to the number buzzle.

dialogue.speaker: Doctor
dialogue.text: Ah, that explains why the shirt has no pocket.
